# Lead forms → Google Apps Script endpoint (writes submissions e.g. to a Sheet).
# The endpoint URL is PUBLIC (it ships in the page JS), kept in an env var so it
# is easy to change per environment.
#
# 1. Deploy your Apps Script as a Web app (Execute as: Me · Who has access: Anyone);
#    copy the URL like https://script.google.com/macros/s/…/exec
# 2. In Cloudflare Pages → project → Settings → Environment variables, add:
#       PUBLIC_LEADS_ENDPOINT = <your …/exec URL>   (for Production AND Preview)
# 3. Re-deploy.
PUBLIC_LEADS_ENDPOINT=
